Class Simple

  • java.lang.Object
    • provided.Simple
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.github.robocup_atan.atan.model.ControllerPlayer

    public class Simple
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.github.robocup_atan.atan.model.ControllerPlayer
    A simple controller. It implements the following simple behaviour. If the client sees nothing (it might be out of the field) it turns 180 degree. If the client sees the own goal and the distance is less than 40 and greater than 10 it turns to his own goal and dashes. If it cannot see the own goal but can see the ball it turns to the ball and dashes. If it sees anything but not the ball or the own goals it dashes a little bit and turns a fixed amount of degree to the right.
